+## 8. Debug/Trace Macros
+- **arguments inside `DP`, `DPN`, `DPH`, `DT`, `DTN`, `DTH` must be comma-separated**.
+
+Correct:
+```cpp
+DT(2, "req: wid=" << wid << ", pc=0x" << std::hex << pc << std::endl);
+```
+
+Incorrect (space-separated entries):
+```cpp
+DT(2, "req: wid=" << wid << " pc=0x" << std::hex << pc << std::endl);
 ```
\ No newline at end of file
